ttps://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/44/size6/37361c6a3d23feb30eaf9dd9e66e4fa0.jpg","text":"ସେ କାନ୍ଦିବାକୁ ଲାଗିଲା।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/45/size6/c6dd7e9100c59475dfff669aea42043c.jpg","text":"ମାଙ୍କଡ଼ଟିଏ ଆସି\nତା'\nଗୋଡ଼\nଆଉଁଷି ଦେଲା।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/46/size6/b7c5a2321034eefd58064417dbed109c.jpg","text":"ଭାଲୁଅଜା\nତାକୁ କୋଳରେ ଧରିଲେ।\nସେ\nଚୁପ୍ ହେଲାନି।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/47/size6/4b9d3c5ef3ff7f193bbc57ee9873948a.jpg","text":"ତା'\nମାଆ ଆସିଲା । କହିଲା, \"ଦେଖ୍, ପଥରକୁ ବାଡ଼େଇଲି।\"","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/48/size6/fa745053851dd15865fd30a47599ad37.jpg","text":"ହରିଣଛୁଆ\nକହିଲା, \"ତାକୁ ବାଡ଼ାନି। ସେ ବି କାନ୍ଦିବ।\"\nମାଆ ହସିଦେଲା।\nସେ ବି ହସିଦେଲା।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":57}}